      </div>

      <div xml:id="Aink3">
        <lg type="edition">
          <l> vāḻi yātaṉ vāḻi yaviṉi</l>
          <l> pālpala vūṟuka pakaṭupala ciṟakka</l>
          <l> veṉavēṭ ṭōḷē yāyē yāmē</l>
          <l> vittiya vuḻavar nelloṭu peyarum</l>
          <l> pūkkaña lūraṉ ṟaṉmaṉai </l>
          <l> vāḻkkai polika veṉavēṭ ṭēmē. </l>
        </lg>
        <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">

          <l> 'May Ātaṉ prosper, may Aviṉi prosper.</l>
          <l> Let many [drops of] milk trickle, let many bulls grow,'</l>
          <l> thus wants our mother. We:</l>
          <l> 'The house of the man from the village dense with flowers,</l>
          <l> where the ploughmen who have sown come back with paddy:</l>
          <l> let [its] livelihood flourish, thus we want.</l>


        </lg>
      </div>
    </body>
